<topic id="sharepoint-actions-at-folder-level">
  <title><?oxy_comment_start author="steven_higgs" timestamp="20160307T162847+0200" comment="Merged or no longer needed. Moved to not_used folder.  "?>Actions
    Available at Folder Level<?oxy_comment_end?></title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>SharePoint Connection<indexterm>actions at folder level</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>The contextual menu of a folder node in a SharePoint connection in the <uicontrol>Data Source
        Explorer</uicontrol> view contains the following actions:</p>
    <dl>
      <dlentry id="new_file">
        <dt><uicontrol>New File</uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Creates a new file on the server in the current folder.</dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry conref="webdav-actions-at-connection-level.dita#webdav-actions-at-connection-level/new_folder">
        <dt/>
        <dd/>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry id="import_folders">
        <dt><uicontrol>Import Folders</uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Imports folders on the server.</dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry>
        <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/AddFile16.gif" id="image_aq2_d2w_sr"/>Import
            Files</uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Allows you to add a new file on the server in the current folder.</dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry id="cut_webdav">
        <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Cut16.png" id="image_ipp_4z1_5r"/>Cut</uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Removes the current selection and places it in the clipboard.</dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry id="copy_webdav">
        <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Copy16.png" id="image_c5l_2st_tr"/>Copy</uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Copies the current selection.</dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry>
        <dt><uicontrol>
            <image href="../img/Paste16.png" id="image_hwv_nqt_tr"/>Paste</uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Pastes the copied selection.</dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry id="rename_webdav">
        <dt><uicontrol>Rename</uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Allows you to change the name of the selected folder.</dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry id="delete_webdav">
        <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/RemoveSelected16.gif" placement="inline"
            />Delete</uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Removes the selected folder.</dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry id="refreseh_webdav">
        <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Refresh16.png" id="image_o31_y2w_sr"
          />Refresh</uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Refreshes the sub-tree of the selected node.</dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry conref="webdav-actions-at-connection-level.dita#webdav-actions-at-connection-level/find_replace_in_files">
        <dt/>
        <dd/>
      </dlentry>
    </dl>
